{"tid":61314,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公平地比較籃球同足球(2)","createTime":"2016-12-31T06:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-05T13:24:59.000Z","uid":41411,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc67af181707115189a1f911674abe2d22dde19d","tid":61314,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"從各方面去比較籃球同足球 大家唔好再嘈黎嘈去<br />\n<br />\n1. 現役最佳球員既身體質素<br />\n籃球 - Lebron James <br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/4b/d6/e1/4bd6e11bf10419a2980f325ba74bbe39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F4b%2Fd6%2Fe1%2F4bd6e11bf10419a2980f325ba74bbe39.jpg&h=9f352131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n足球 - Lionel Messi<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/55/59/d5/5559d53facc4849bb12c0d67d3acd9b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F55%2F59%2Fd5%2F5559d53facc4849bb12c0d67d3acd9b3.jpg&h=6782dc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">結論: 足球岩身型弱小既人玩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 場地數量 - 以香港為例<br />\n籃球有507個 <br />\n足球草地連硬地有316個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">結論: 足球無籃球咁受歡迎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 裝備<br />\n籃球 - 得1對籃球鞋 頭帶臂套只有少部分人用 而且作用不大<br />\n<br />\n足球 - 波鞋, 護脛, 冬天戴手套, 龍門要戴龍門手套<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">結論: 足球員比較怕受傷 係溫室長大既小花</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 體能需求<br />\n籃球 - 要不斷來回跑進攻同防守 好多身體碰撞 就算場地有冷氣,對髒能需求都十分大<br />\n足球 - 場地及人數多 較多時間可以散步 現今最佳球員美斯常於場上散步, 大雨少少就會腰斬賽事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">結論: 足球員唔需要體能 老人家食飽飽亦可以落場參與賽事 順便散步</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0b563528226ef3edd413dc723fbc2cc68133d07","tid":61314,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"5. 戰術運用<br />\n籃球 - 多變既戰術, 適當時間會暫停再改變戰術, 係鬥智鬥技術既運動<br />\n<br />\n足球 - 落到場就由得足球員自己踢, 後衛中場前鋒經常唔係企係自己個位置, 所以所謂既陣容係廢, 教練只有換人時先有作用<br />\n<br />\n結論: <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">籃球對戰術既掌握比較重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n6. 觀眾享受程度<br />\n籃球 - 節奏緊湊, 每節既休息時間唔會太長, 經常性會有絕殺既情況, 而且唔會有打和 可以真正分到勝負<br />\n<br />\n足球 - 節奏緩慢, 球員散步時間較多, 不時踢到120分鍾仍然無入球 觀眾會好悶 而且經常性打和 性質上較似獎門人遊戲<br />\n<br />\n結論: <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇籃球比賽會好睇好多 睇足球會好易瞓著</span></span>"},{"pid":"f2c9d3d074e84afb71529665804616ac29806536","tid":61314,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"咁都1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2818ca71db555cb5bc1ab3d220617f43966d1d4","tid":61314,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"7. 比賽公平程度<br />\n<br />\n籃球 - 當有爭議既判決出現時 會有3名球證一齊睇回帶 再商討決判, 好少假賽發生<br />\n<br />\n足球 - 主要判決都由一位球證判決 好多時都有黑哨既情況, 著名既有2002年世界盃黑哨事件. 已經周不時發生入左當未入 未入當入左<br />\n<br />\n結論: 籃球係公平公正公開既運動 足球容易被控制 經常踢假波 違反體育精神"},{"pid":"7dcb92884aac383388faaa271ff6fa330337ca1f","tid":61314,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不服來辯!</span></span>"},{"pid":"29efb279427fd1b6ff75dac8d07949b340cc31cc","tid":61314,"uid":60492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個國家most popular sports =blueball而高過足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kdnrq461\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkdnrq461&h=96c9379d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jbcm1z0t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjbcm1z0t&h=5c5e1f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c486831799bd6c0a8f498ddfc49d8739dad5884","tid":61314,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"終於有個理性公平post <br />\n支持樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fdc72014af1ef796ab16a8ed830af3adad455e","tid":61314,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7e3196dc55e21eaf4d8517824b5eb12d7f9d4f","tid":61314,"uid":22584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"我凈係知我打籃球個班fd個個有女 踢波個班真係無邊個有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d6cba040cbd3cfbff0986f114a57d208ae3ea8","tid":61314,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我凈係知我打籃球個班fd個個有女 踢波個班真係無邊個有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d13fb748a00c4c04b00579e13bbe63b6fd9a9f3","tid":61314,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"8. 目標<br />\n籃球 - 籃球員目標將球投入一個直徑1.5ft左右既籃框以求得分<br />\n<br />\n足球 - 足球員目標將球攻入一個8yd x 8ft的龍門架以求得分<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">結論: 籃球員人生目光淺窄，足球員目標宏大、胸襟廣闊</span></span>"}]}